title: Education software firm Instructure files for IPO
text:
Related: Markets, Technology Education software firm Instructure files for IPO 
Oct 9 Education software company Instructre Inc on Friday filed with U.S. regulators for an initial public offering of common stock. 
Morgan Stanley, Goldman Sachs & Co and Jefferies are among the underwriters for the offering, the company said in a filing with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission. ( 1.usa.gov/1WRoKXP ) (Reporting by Kshitiz Goliya in Bengaluru; Editing by Savio D'Souza) Trending On Reuters
